==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: outright
<hw>out"right`</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Downright; plain; unqualified;
utter; straight-out; <as>as, an <ex>outright</ex> lie</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flat-out, out-and-out.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>outright</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: outright
<hw>out"right`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Immediately; without delay; at once; <as>as, he was killed
<ex>outright</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Completely; utterly.</def> <rj><au>Cardinal
Manning.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outring</ent>⟦br⟧
